#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:2 b7a018f2ecb64dd3a44aa4783a429e97
msgid "系统"
msgstr "System"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:17 f1daf8b5077c48e3ac5604f56a8b2421
msgid "如果我的应⽤不需要看⻔狗，如何关闭看⻔狗？"
msgstr "How can I disable the watchdog if my application does not need it?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:19 8ac58774df3f47e7a008098d6f55b1a9
msgid "当前 SDK 仅⽀持关闭软件看⻔狗，⽀持同时喂软硬件看⻔狗。可以通过如下⽅式防⽌执⾏时间过⻓的⽤户程序导致看⻔狗复位"
msgstr "The current SDK only supports disabling the software watchdog, and supports feeding both the software and hardware watchdogs at the same time. You can prevent user programs with long execution times from causing a watchdog reset in the following ways:"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:21 c675ed0f70954055aa40b3f5a81262ca
msgid "如果⼀个程序段运⾏时间在触发软件看⻔狗和触发硬件看⻔狗复位之间，则可通过 system_soft_wdt_stop() 的⽅式关闭软件看⻔狗，在程序段执⾏完毕后⽤ system_soft_wdt_restart() 重新打开软件看⻔狗。"
msgstr "If a program segment runs for a duration between the software watchdog trigger time and the hardware watchdog reset trigger time, you can disable the software watchdog by calling system_soft_wdt_stop(), and re-enable it with system_soft_wdt_restart() after the program segment finishes execution."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:22 0f8e5d236c6b4b13aea97c130f221c57
msgid "可以通过在程序段中添加 system_soft_wdt_feed() 来进⾏喂软硬件狗操作，防⽌软硬件看⻔狗复位。"
msgstr "You can add system_soft_wdt_feed() in the program segment to feed both the software and hardware watchdogs, preventing software/hardware watchdog resets."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:23 dc6d296be88343fc9e3e9169139f9d33
msgid "硬件看⻔狗中断时间为 0.8 *2048 ms，即 1638.4 s，中断后处理时间为 0.8* 8192 ms，即 6553.6 ms。"
msgstr "The hardware watchdog interrupt time is 0.8 * 2048 ms, that is, 1638.4 ms. The post-interrupt handling time is 0.8 * 8192 ms, that is, 6553.6 ms."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:24 c410cd3b57f24a59af89a573422ef8b6
msgid "其中中断处理后时间为硬件看⻔狗中断发⽣后，需要进⾏喂狗操作的时间，如果超过该时间，即会触发硬件看⻔狗复位。"
msgstr "The post-interrupt handling time is the time window after the hardware watchdog interrupt occurs during which the watchdog must be fed. If this time is exceeded, a hardware watchdog reset will be triggered."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:25 870431122be8437da5e09fb17dde9370
msgid "因此，在仅有硬件看⻔狗的情况下，⼀个程序段如果运⾏时间超过 6553.6 ms，即有可能触发硬件看⻔狗复位，若超过 8192 ms 则⼀定会触发复位。"
msgstr "Therefore, when only the hardware watchdog is enabled, if a program segment runs for more than 6553.6 ms, it may trigger a hardware watchdog reset; if it exceeds 8192 ms, it will definitely trigger a reset."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:26 fa5a9bb2187c4a47ae9efaf4c5426322
msgid "软件看⻔狗建⽴在 MAC timer 以及系统调度之上，中断时间为 1600 ms，中断后处理时间 1600 ms。"
msgstr "The software watchdog is based on the MAC timer and system scheduling. Its interrupt time is 1600 ms, and the post-interrupt handling time is 1600 ms."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:27 29a3b98e922b4a20b86980a5c1742ed1
msgid "因此，在有软件+硬件看⻔狗的情况下，⼀个程序段如果运⾏时间超过 1600 ms，即有可能会触发软件看⻔狗复位，若超过 3200 ms 则⼀定会触发复位。"
msgstr "Therefore, when both the software and hardware watchdogs are enabled, if a program segment runs for more than 1600 ms, it may trigger a software watchdog reset; if it exceeds 3200 ms, it will definitely trigger a reset."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:32 2e05332ddea14ea184d2ffcf3d88cb0c
msgid "RTOS SDK 和 Non-OS SDK 有何区别？"
msgstr "What are the differences between RTOS SDK and Non-OS SDK?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:34 46c65b18de55433f9c49a87f1e58269a
msgid "主要差异点如下："
msgstr "The main differences are as follows:"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:36 7b342eff16424b1a9da30ac3f63444c5
msgid "**Non-OS SDK**"
msgstr "**Non-OS SDK**"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:38 0d109bf626754df0a3335be72f5d67cb
msgid "Non-OS SDK 主要使⽤定时器和回调函数的⽅式实现各个功能事件的嵌套，达到特定条件下触发特定功能函数的⽬的。Non-OS SDK 使⽤ espconn 接⼝实现⽹络操作， ⽤户需要按照 espconn 接⼝的使⽤规则进⾏软件开发。"
msgstr "The Non-OS SDK mainly uses timers and callback functions to implement nested functional events, so that specific functional functions are triggered under specific conditions. The Non-OS SDK uses the espconn interface for network operations. Users need to develop software according to the usage rules of the espconn interface."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:40 2132c9ac513747adba31a33be68f697a
msgid "**RTOS SDK**"
msgstr "**RTOS SDK**"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:42 f0716425e1e84637a026841477c1c9d4
msgid "RTOS 版本 SDK 使⽤ freeRTOS 系统，引⼊ OS 多任务处理的机制，⽤户可以使⽤ freeRTOS 的标准接⼝实现资源管理、循环操作、任务内延时、任务间信息传递和同步等⾯向任务流程的设计⽅式。具体接⼝使⽤⽅法参考 freeRTOS 官⽅⽹站的使⽤说明或者 USING THE FREERTOS REAL TIME KERNEL - A Practical Guide 这本书中的介绍。"
msgstr "The RTOS SDK uses the freeRTOS system and introduces the OS multitasking mechanism. Users can use standard freeRTOS interfaces to implement task-oriented process designs such as resource management, loop operations, delays within tasks, inter-task message passing, and synchronization. For detailed interface usage, refer to the instructions on the official freeRTOS website or the book USING THE FREERTOS REAL TIME KERNEL - A Practical Guide."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:43 659199478d51479cbdd3567d8f68c59e
msgid "RTOS 版本 SDK 的⽹络操作接⼝是标准 lwIP API，同时提供了 BSD Socket API 接⼝的封装实现，⽤户可以直接按照 socket API 的使⽤⽅式来开发软件应⽤，也可以直接编译运⾏其他平台的标准 Socket 应⽤，有效降低平台切换的学习成本。"
msgstr "The network operation interface of the RTOS SDK is the standard lwIP API. It also provides an encapsulated implementation of the BSD Socket API. Users can directly develop software applications according to the socket API usage method, or directly compile and run standard Socket applications from other platforms, effectively reducing the learning cost of platform migration."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:44 738b89fbc6cd458a99517b6b51112f81
msgid "RTOS 版本 SDK 引⼊了 cJSON 库，使⽤该库函数可以更加⽅便的实现对 JSON 数据包的解析。"
msgstr "The RTOS SDK introduces the cJSON library. Using this library makes it easier to parse JSON data packets."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:45 363c67f89ead44379a40af82879402c5
msgid "RTOS 版本兼容 Non-OS SDK 中的 Wi-Fi 接⼝、SmartConfig 接⼝、Sniffer 相关接⼝、系统接⼝、定时器接⼝、FOTA 接⼝和外围驱动接⼝，不⽀持 AT 实现。"
msgstr "The RTOS version is compatible with the Wi-Fi interfaces, SmartConfig interfaces, Sniffer-related interfaces, system interfaces, timer interfaces, FOTA interfaces, and peripheral driver interfaces in the Non-OS SDK, but it does not support AT implementation."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:50 cfbabc7279104a1a9fb06d0721f19b33
msgid "ESP8266 启动时 LOG 输出 ets_main.c 有哪些原因？"
msgstr "What are the possible reasons for ESP8266 outputting ets_main.c in the startup LOG?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:52 f7ce08e0784a464196a316a3da622654
msgid "ESP8266 启动时打印 ``ets_main.c`` ，表示没有可运⾏的程序区，⽆法运⾏；遇到这种问题时，请检查烧录时的 bin ⽂件和烧录地址是否正确。"
msgstr "When ESP8266 prints ``ets_main.c`` during startup, it means that there is no runnable program area and it cannot run. When encountering this issue, check whether the bin file and the flashing address are correct."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:57 19346792095c4b0babd1b0da79fb3b1f
msgid "ESP8266 编译 Non-OS SDK 时 IRAM_ATTR 错误是什么原因？"
msgstr "What causes the IRAM_ATTR error when compiling the ESP8266 Non-OS SDK?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:59 94fec15501f3497892746ec78c6012de
msgid "如果需要在 IRAM 中执⾏功能，就不需要加 ``ICACHE_FLASH_ATTR`` 的宏，那么该功能就是放在 IRAM 中执⾏。"
msgstr "If a function needs to execute in IRAM, you do not need to add the ``ICACHE_FLASH_ATTR`` macro. In that case, the function will be placed in IRAM for execution."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:64 e750f1f5b27149a89f612db6577bbfcd
msgid "ESP8266 main 函数在哪里？"
msgstr "Where is the main function of ESP8266?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:66 813305538c65425b93c2b244b607fd42
msgid "ESP8266 用户 SDK 部分没有 main 函数。main 函数处于 一级 bootloader 并且固化在芯片 ROM 中， 用于引导二级 bootloader。二级 bootloader 入口函数为 ets_main，启动后会加载用户应用中的 user_init，引导至用户程序。"
msgstr "The user SDK part of ESP8266 does not have a main function. The main function is located in the first-stage bootloader and is solidified in the chip ROM. It is used to boot the second-stage bootloader. The entry function of the second-stage bootloader is ets_main. After startup, it loads user_init from the user application and boots into the user program."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:71 9b62d60e168d48678c31b7e4f87284ec
msgid "ESP8266 partition-tables 特殊注意点？"
msgstr "Special notes about ESP8266 partition-tables?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:73 f540504fc88d471bb1489332fcc5fc83
msgid "ESP8266 partition-tables 相对 ESP32 对于 ota 分区有一定的特殊要求，这是由于 ESP8266 cache 特性导致。详情参考 `ESP8266 partition-tables 偏移与空间 <https://docs.espressif.com/projects/esp8266-rtos-sdk/en/latest/api-guides/partition-tables.html#offset-size>`_。"
msgstr "Compared with ESP32, ESP8266 partition-tables have certain special requirements for OTA partitions. This is caused by the ESP8266 cache characteristics. For details, refer to `ESP8266 partition-tables offset and size <https://docs.espressif.com/projects/esp8266-rtos-sdk/en/latest/api-guides/partition-tables.html#offset-size>`_."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:78 8f3d8073fdd74cbda3f148c5f4c5d045
msgid "应用层与底层的 bin 文件可以分开编译码？"
msgstr "Can the bin files of the application layer and the underlying layer be compiled separately?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:80 76d6e6ab6ab8479db3ddc710cb1c170f
msgid "不⽀持分开编译。"
msgstr "Separate compilation is not supported."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:85 000dc64f5f014c0285b1ced3ff559523
msgid "ESP32 模组 flash 使用 80 Mhz 有什么注意事项吗 ？"
msgstr "Are there any precautions for using 80 MHz flash on ESP32 modules?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:87 06649c3ff0e04df499bf0e8fddae6000
msgid "乐鑫模组发售前已经过稳定性测试，测试可以支持 80 MHz 频率。根据稳定性测试数据，80 MHz 的频率不会影响使用寿命和稳定性。"
msgstr "Espressif modules have undergone stability testing before release, and the tests show that they can support an 80 MHz frequency. According to the stability test data, an 80 MHz frequency does not affect service life or stability."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:92 b53d98161640466895acdf49e63bf91f
msgid "ESP32 系统软件复位 API？"
msgstr "ESP32 system software reset API?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:94 5c916b0f74224707a114f0a006b69177
msgid "软件复位 API：``esp_restart()``。"
msgstr "Software reset API: ``esp_restart()``."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:99 14befc106c66419883dd29dbc899afc8
msgid "使用 esp-idf 按汇编操作寄存器，是否涉及到调用不可编辑的库文件？"
msgstr "When using esp-idf to operate registers with assembly, does it involve calling non-editable library files?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:101 935b985f417f4b71a72d48ff480f32f8
msgid "如果单纯使用读写寄存器指令或者汇编指令，不存在调用库文件的问题。如果调用 esp-idf 预制的函数，则可能会遇到调用 lib 函数的情况。"
msgstr "If only register read/write instructions or assembly instructions are used, there is no issue of calling library files. If pre-built esp-idf functions are called, calls to lib functions may occur."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:102 ed6b49824f7748aa804a19bb710b4d84
msgid "不推荐在 ESP32 中使用汇编操作，如果部分场景想要提高速度，可以读写寄存器来完成部分操作。"
msgstr "It is not recommended to use assembly operations on ESP32. If you want to improve speed in some scenarios, you can complete some operations by reading and writing registers."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:107 95a246512e974bf397ecdb0feaffd376
msgid "使用 ESP-IDF 测试程序，如何设置可在单核模组上下载程序？"
msgstr "How to configure an ESP-IDF test program so that it can be downloaded to a single-core module?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:109 df5e504c7b934184be2322f8210675d6
msgid "程序编译时，使用 make menuconfig 指令进入配置界面，进行如下配置，可在单核模组上下载程序；在配置界面中，按键 Y 为启动，N 为关闭。"
msgstr "During program compilation, use the make menuconfig command to enter the configuration interface. Configure as follows to download the program to a single-core module. In the configuration interface, key Y enables an option, and N disables it."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:111 54dce0badcd74b7e8bfdafa58df7f5e1
msgid "``Component config --> FreeRTOS --> Run FreeRTOS only on first core``"
msgstr "``Component config --> FreeRTOS --> Run FreeRTOS only on first core``"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:116 e16ed87a12134598861fa6c5fdf002aa
msgid "使用 esp-idf，如何使能 ESP32 的双核模式？"
msgstr "How to enable dual-core mode on ESP32 when using esp-idf?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:118 922aa3f2b5e54e3bbc2614ca2264e30f
msgid "esp-idf 一般情况下默认配置的是双核模式，您可以在 menuconfig 中进行单双核的修改：menuconfig -> Component config -> FreeRTOS -> Run。"
msgstr "In general, esp-idf is configured for dual-core mode by default. You can modify single-core/dual-core settings in menuconfig: menuconfig -> Component config -> FreeRTOS -> Run."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:120 b7a15b51fd724a1db52efff796d19085
msgid "FreeRTOS only on first core 使能即为单核，未使能默认双核。"
msgstr "Enabling FreeRTOS only on first core means single-core mode; if it is not enabled, the default is dual-core mode."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:125 6739ea5be4d34743b39c4b213a1423c1
msgid "使用 ESP32-D0WD 芯片是否可以存储用户程序？"
msgstr "Can the ESP32-D0WD chip store user programs?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:127 d9269306e13d49f5a5bf227dd624487a
msgid "不可以，用户程序必须使用外挂 Flash 进行存储，片上 ROM 不能存储用户程序。ROM 内存放的程序为芯片一级 bootloader，为了保护出厂程序不被破坏，该区域为只读存储。"
msgstr "No. User programs must be stored in external Flash. The on-chip ROM cannot store user programs. The program stored in ROM is the chip’s first-stage bootloader. To protect the factory program from being damaged, this area is read-only storage."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:132 592d496305564d608a3dcb54dec34166
msgid "ESP32 进入低功耗模式时， PSRAM 中的数据会丢失吗？"
msgstr "Will data in PSRAM be lost when ESP32 enters low-power mode?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:134 e016be7577f04184ae2b439b9a9b0d8a
msgid "Modem-sleep/Light-sleep 模式时，PSRAM 中的数据不会丢失。"
msgstr "In Modem-sleep/Light-sleep mode, data in PSRAM will not be lost."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:135 268971379bdb47ca9d164444578785a0
msgid "Deep-sleep 模式时，CPU 和大部分外设都会掉电，PSRAM 的数据会丢失。"
msgstr "In Deep-sleep mode, the CPU and most peripherals are powered down, and data in PSRAM will be lost."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:140 8ff182da3ae74c0581f224beb566a81d
msgid "请问 ESP32 CPU 系统时间是否由系统滴答时钟生成？精度如何？"
msgstr "Is the ESP32 CPU system time generated by the system tick clock? What is its accuracy?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:142 63ed29a956d44e3c877a5583c26d5984
msgid "CPU 系统时间是由 esp_timer 内部的 64 位硬件定时器 CONFIG_ESP_TIMER_IMPL 产生的，是微秒级的时间分辨率。 参见 `说明 <https://docs.espressif.com/projects/esp-idf/zh_CN/latest/esp32/api-reference/system/esp_timer.html?highlight=esp_timer_get_time#high-resolution-timer>`_。"
msgstr "The CPU system time is generated by the 64-bit hardware timer CONFIG_ESP_TIMER_IMPL inside esp_timer, with microsecond-level time resolution. See `description <https://docs.espressif.com/projects/esp-idf/zh_CN/latest/esp32/api-reference/system/esp_timer.html?highlight=esp_timer_get_time#high-resolution-timer>`_."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:148 532a76711fcc42bf9d06744a479b06ab
msgid "ESP32 的 flash 和 psram 的时钟频率如何修改？"
msgstr "How to modify the clock frequency of ESP32 flash and PSRAM?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:150 1ef216e236ec4af49ba5bec682610035
msgid "在 menuconfig 中修改。 - flash 时钟频率：menuconfig -> Serial flasher config -> Flash SPI speed。 - PSRAM 时钟频率：Component config -> ESP32-specific -> SPI RAM config -> Set RAM clock speed。"
msgstr "Modify them in menuconfig. - Flash clock frequency: menuconfig -> Serial flasher config -> Flash SPI speed. - PSRAM clock frequency: Component config -> ESP32-specific -> SPI RAM config -> Set RAM clock speed."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:157 bb1a2da5b886464b82e4640065358511
msgid "使用 ESP32-SOLO-1 模组，esp-idf 如何设置可在单核模组上运行？"
msgstr "How to configure esp-idf so that it can run on the ESP32-SOLO-1 single-core module?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:159 3897a32fd23d443884fb5b5244591d63
msgid "使用 menuconfig 指令进入配置界面，Component config  -->  FreeRTOS  -->  Run FreeRTOS only on first core（启动此选项）可在单核模组上运行下载。"
msgstr "Use the menuconfig command to enter the configuration interface. Enable Component config --> FreeRTOS --> Run FreeRTOS only on first core, and the program can run and be downloaded on a single-core module."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:164 1ec2798c2a194d2eac395990a62c57f8
msgid "esp-idf 是否可以配置 time_t 为 64 bit ？ （现在是 32 bit）"
msgstr "Can esp-idf configure time_t as 64 bit? It is currently 32 bit."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:166 95025dd774424fb58af700b6898ac60d
msgid "当前暂时不支持，预计在 release/v4.2 或更高版本种支持。如果配置支持 time_t 64 bit 自定义工具链，可以使能 make menuconfig 中 SDK tool configuration -> SDK_TOOLCHAIN_SUPPORTS_TIME_WIDE_64_BITS 。"
msgstr "This is currently not supported. It is expected to be supported in release/v4.2 or later. If a custom toolchain supports 64-bit time_t, you can enable SDK tool configuration -> SDK_TOOLCHAIN_SUPPORTS_TIME_WIDE_64_BITS in make menuconfig."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:171 2972d4497213418db8307e93c3b14267
msgid "固件如何区分主芯片是 ESP8285 还是 ESP8266？"
msgstr "How does firmware distinguish whether the main chip is ESP8285 or ESP8266?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:173 2590853c4191481096557d7eae9e5b0e
msgid "通常使用外部工具 `esptool <https://github.com/espressif/esptool>`_ 来读取芯片类型。可以在固件中根据 python 代码示例，读取芯片对应寄存器位，并进计算判断得出。"
msgstr "Usually, the external tool `esptool <https://github.com/espressif/esptool>`_ is used to read the chip type. In firmware, you can read the corresponding chip register bits and calculate the result according to the Python code example."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:189 5efafae0c79d48aa90c984229cfeb6f3
msgid "ESP32 能否以动态库的方式加载库文件运行？"
msgstr "Can ESP32 load and run library files as dynamic libraries?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:191 500639394dfd4751a74983b9e67ca11e
msgid "ESP32 不支持动态库的方式加载库文件，只支持靜态库。"
msgstr "ESP32 does not support loading library files as dynamic libraries; it only supports static libraries."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:196 8098c0dbf73f436a99ca5000dad62be4
msgid "ESP32 如何减小系统对 IRAM 内存的占用？"
msgstr "How to reduce ESP32 system IRAM memory usage?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:198 9a5ea8582ed64835b94f03c5eeaf89d5
msgid "请将 mencuofnig -> Component config -> LWIP -> Enable LWIP IRAM optimization (键\"N\" 禁用) 配置选项禁用。"
msgstr "Disable the configuration option menuconfig -> Component config -> LWIP -> Enable LWIP IRAM optimization (press \"N\" to disable)."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:199 188193455e324be78b5bd9cf4537d68d
msgid "请更改 menuconfig -> Compiler option -> Optimization Level -> Optimize for size (-Os) 中的配置选项。"
msgstr "Change the configuration option in menuconfig -> Compiler option -> Optimization Level -> Optimize for size (-Os)."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:200 be8420205dd64ea29d39a2a778028506
msgid "请将 menuconfig -> Component config -> wifi 中的配置选项中的 WiFi IRAM speed optimization (N) 和 WiFi RX IRAM speed optimization (N) 配置选项禁用。"
msgstr "Disable the WiFi IRAM speed optimization (N) and WiFi RX IRAM speed optimization (N) configuration options in menuconfig -> Component config -> wifi."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:204 a8f58db816e64bd5837aec81303ed4a4
msgid "ESP32 芯片低电压复位阈值是多少？"
msgstr "What is the low-voltage reset threshold of the ESP32 chip?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:206 4a3219e88ac440509edd67c95a4b4ed9
msgid "欠压复位电压阈值范围在 2.43V ~ 2.80 V 之间，可在 menuconfig -> Component config -> ESP32-specific -> Brownout voltage level 中进行设置。"
msgstr "The brownout reset voltage threshold range is 2.43 V ~ 2.80 V. It can be configured in menuconfig -> Component config -> ESP32-specific -> Brownout voltage level."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:211 7f5efe34966a41918cea8b70d582df7f
msgid "ESP32 light sleep 例程为何会自动唤醒？"
msgstr "Why does the ESP32 light sleep example wake up automatically?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:213 f93bbac54c464d448cfb280f9b65c163
msgid "light sleep 例程下，默认使用了两种唤醒方式，如下： .. code-block:: c"
msgstr "In the light sleep example, two wake-up methods are enabled by default, as follows: .. code-block:: c"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:216 a131988c5549489fab064471ed2a7856
msgid "esp_sleep_enable_timer_wakeup(2000000);     // 2 秒自动唤醒 esp_sleep_enable_gpio_wakeup();             // GPIO 唤醒"
msgstr "esp_sleep_enable_timer_wakeup(2000000);     // Automatically wake up after 2 seconds esp_sleep_enable_gpio_wakeup();             // GPIO wake-up"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:219 a9fa7c897649466d9d96b48410f302c1
msgid "GPIO 唤醒默认是 GPIO0 低有效唤醒，GPIO0 拉低则为唤醒状态，GPIO0 释放则自动进入 light sleep 模式。 若需要长时间保存 light sleep 模式，可以将 2 秒自动唤醒屏蔽，仅开启 GPIO 唤醒。"
msgstr "GPIO wake-up defaults to GPIO0 active-low wake-up. Pulling GPIO0 low puts it into the wake-up state; releasing GPIO0 makes it automatically enter light sleep mode. If you need to maintain light sleep mode for a long time, you can disable the 2-second automatic wake-up and only enable GPIO wake-up."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:225 24378f7fbb3744e89e1156c314f3379f
msgid "ESP32 deep_sleep例程测试，为何当 const int wakeup_time_sec = 3600时，程序 crash 出现死循环？"
msgstr "Why does the ESP32 deep_sleep example crash and enter a dead loop when const int wakeup_time_sec = 3600?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:227 a6be807e223a4da4ab0c80d985055723
msgid "程序 crash 原因是 int 类型参数 `wakeup_time_sec` 在 wakeup_time_sec * 1000000 在运算时溢出。"
msgstr "The program crash is caused by overflow of the int-type parameter `wakeup_time_sec` during the calculation wakeup_time_sec * 1000000."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:237 6dfb3e6bc781494f9c2c447f2fb67d87
msgid "ESP32 有几种系统复位方式？"
msgstr "How many system reset methods does ESP32 have?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:239 57b7c39f1bb44062b1d074363c29e652
msgid "有“芯片上电复位”、“RWDT 系统复位”、“欠压复位” 3 种系统复位方式。"
msgstr "There are three system reset methods: “chip power-on reset”, “RWDT system reset”, and “brownout reset”."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:240 fb33b36bd3b347eb95c4f17781b09269
msgid "具体说明参见 `ESP32 技术规格书 <https://www.espressif.com/sites/default/files/documentation/esp32_technical_reference_manual_cn.pdf>`__ 4.1.2 复位源章节。"
msgstr "For details, refer to Chapter 4.1.2 Reset Sources in the `ESP32 Technical Reference Manual <https://www.espressif.com/sites/default/files/documentation/esp32_technical_reference_manual_cn.pdf>`__."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:245 a5ff0abe84ce4a3784caafde140b7259
msgid "ESP8266-NONOS-V3.0 版本的 SDK，报错如下，是什么原因？"
msgstr "What causes the following error in ESP8266-NONOS-V3.0 SDK?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:252 73d4be9a1e3e455ba6d2c7c80e5aa1cc
msgid "导致出现 E:M 开头的 LOG 是由于剩余内存不足。"
msgstr "LOGs starting with E:M are caused by insufficient remaining memory."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:257 dd4cdd67cc214ca28714b19c43f86a96
msgid "ESP32 是否可以完整使用 8MB PSRAM 内存？"
msgstr "Can ESP32 fully use 8 MB PSRAM?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:259 3020ab9a5bf14f8e828375ca89fee38d
msgid "ESP32 可完整使用 8MB PSRAM 内存。"
msgstr "ESP32 can fully use 8 MB PSRAM."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:260 d45f2f46a5fe46a7a49caa0d5d877396
msgid "由于 cache 最大映射空间为 4MB，所以仅支持 4MB psram 映射使用，剩余空间可以使用 API 操作使用。"
msgstr "Since the maximum cache mapping space is 4 MB, only 4 MB PSRAM mapping is supported. The remaining space can be used through API operations."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:261 7cc46d248ab642dcb16a5d5fc1e85ccb
msgid "参考示例 [himem](https://github.com/espressif/esp-idf/tree/master/examples/system/himem)。"
msgstr "Reference example: [himem](https://github.com/espressif/esp-idf/tree/master/examples/system/himem)."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:266 2e7baecb169147169334b2d2cb4b3e40
msgid "ESP8266 AT 连接 AP 后，系统默认进入 modem-sleep，但电流未明显下降有哪些原因？"
msgstr "After ESP8266 AT connects to an AP, the system enters modem-sleep by default, but why does the current not drop significantly?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:268 6b4c196b95604bc1b45d40be45deea41
msgid "AT 固件连接 AP 后，ESP8266 会进入自动 modem-sleep 模式，功耗大约会在 15mA ~ 70mA 之间波动。"
msgstr "After the AT firmware connects to an AP, ESP8266 enters automatic modem-sleep mode, and the power consumption fluctuates around 15 mA ~ 70 mA."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:269 7a0b8c09a7b64992bd145c726a8de92b
msgid "如果功耗并没有在 15mA ~ 70mA 之间波动，在示波器中未呈现波形的电流，有以下建议： - 擦除设备 flash 后，重新烧录 AT 固件。 - 抓取网络包分析，是否在当前的网络环境中，是否有频繁发送广播包的设备，可换一个网络环境的路由器（AP）进行测试。"
msgstr "If the power consumption does not fluctuate between 15 mA ~ 70 mA, and no current waveform is observed on the oscilloscope, the following suggestions apply: - Erase the device flash and re-flash the AT firmware. - Capture network packets and analyze whether there are devices frequently sending broadcast packets in the current network environment. You can test with a router (AP) in another network environment."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:276 6bb6f8bfeefc40f681fbe5d9830eabde
msgid "ESP32 是否可以永久更改 MAC 地址？"
msgstr "Can ESP32 permanently change its MAC address?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:278 206bce169e5f4a749b5fc32ba61c0698
msgid "芯片自带的 MAC 地址无法修改。efuse 中支持用户写入自己的 MAC 地址。"
msgstr "The built-in MAC address of the chip cannot be modified. efuse supports writing a user-defined MAC address."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:279 5150c3ad4f6848eaa7e4f09002fe59c9
msgid "在固件中调用 api 可以获取定制 MAC 地址，并且可以设置到系统中替代默认地址。"
msgstr "In the firmware, APIs can be called to obtain the customized MAC address and set it in the system to replace the default address."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:280 a324117eb66a4c7aa821fc3bb76e40c9
msgid "配置参考：`mac-address <https://docs.espressif.com/projects/esp-idf/en/latest/esp32/api-reference/system/system.html#mac-address>`_。"
msgstr "Configuration reference: `mac-address <https://docs.espressif.com/projects/esp-idf/en/latest/esp32/api-reference/system/system.html#mac-address>`_."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:281 d4c6cef647ea4b5fa3a38c3a2f4d18ee
msgid "另外，Espressif 提供在芯片出厂之前，烧录用户提供的 MAC 地址服务。如有需要，可发送邮件至 sales@espressif.com"
msgstr "In addition, Espressif provides a service to burn the user-provided MAC address before the chip leaves the factory. If needed, send an email to sales@espressif.com."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:286 d40188d4b7174fa7ae52a4bd2e378143
msgid "ESP8266 进行 ota 升级时如何校验 all.bin 为非法文件？"
msgstr "How can ESP8266 verify that all.bin is an invalid file during OTA upgrade?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:288 04b60ef78e834203be32ae0ca35dce07
msgid "**问题背景：**"
msgstr "**Background:**"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:290 abeb2e5221f9499b84113face5b5b6ab
msgid "all.bin: 由 bootloader.bin，partition.bin 和 app.bin 合并生成。"
msgstr "all.bin: generated by merging bootloader.bin, partition.bin, and app.bin."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:291 1616ca4614194577afa9be83b1bba97f
msgid "ota.bin: 用于 ota 升级的目标 bin文件。"
msgstr "ota.bin: target bin file used for OTA upgrade."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:293 2482846e0a29470f818ef01659cf3bee
msgid "使用 `simple_ota_example <https://github.com/espressif/ESP8266_RTOS_SDK/tree/master/examples/system/ota/simple_ota_example>`_ 进行 OTA 升级时，误从服务器上下载 all.bin,写入 ota 分区之后，设备会出现反复重启的现象。"
msgstr "When using `simple_ota_example <https://github.com/espressif/ESP8266_RTOS_SDK/tree/master/examples/system/ota/simple_ota_example>`_ for OTA upgrade, if all.bin is mistakenly downloaded from the server and written to the OTA partition, the device will repeatedly reboot."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:295 cb4b70d0aab9457ab352bbf7a48769ce
msgid "**原因分析：**"
msgstr "**Cause analysis:**"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:297 9678d5e5a0d94c0db5650b006512eb38
msgid "代码中未对 all.bin 进行校验，导致将非法的 bin 文件写入 ota 分区。"
msgstr "The code does not verify all.bin, causing an invalid bin file to be written to the OTA partition."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:299 50c62412e8ba435a8d3f70285773514e
msgid "**解决方案：**"
msgstr "**Solution:**"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:301 c3fda1747e5d42a6a1fd695825faeb14
msgid "通过打开 sha256 校验判断 all.bin 为非法 bin 文件，配置路径如下：Component config > App update > [*] Check APP binary data hash after downloading."
msgstr "Enable sha256 verification to determine that all.bin is an invalid bin file. Configuration path: Component config > App update > [*] Check APP binary data hash after downloading."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:306 0e4cdeac4a9d48e0a3a93fa9f6c39a8e
msgid "IDF 版本更新后，更新说明在哪里？"
msgstr "Where can I find the release notes after the IDF version is updated?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:308 7a6f6bdd3e5e4d8bbd36780890797c28
msgid "可以在 Github release note 查看相关说明。链接为: https://github.com/espressif/esp-idf/releases"
msgstr "You can view the relevant notes in the GitHub release notes. Link: https://github.com/espressif/esp-idf/releases"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:313 053b260f3c2641c3ae224d7ff23c8c69
msgid "ESP8266 是否有详细的寄存器⼿册？"
msgstr "Does ESP8266 have a detailed register manual?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:315 6a1587a726994f2085bee0e5488127bd
msgid "请参考 《8266 TRM appendix》部分，链接：https://www.espressif.com/sites/default/files/documentation/esp8266-technical_reference_cn.pdf"
msgstr "Please refer to the “8266 TRM appendix” section. Link: https://www.espressif.com/sites/default/files/documentation/esp8266-technical_reference_cn.pdf"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:320 5ff831aa4d4244fa8020e0df534fd864
msgid "ESP32 开启 Secure Boot 后 无法正常启动 ,出现如下报错，是什么原因？"
msgstr "ESP32 cannot boot normally after Secure Boot is enabled and reports the following error. What is the reason?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:335 5fedc5e76b9f4816b25c1c19c0eb5e7d
msgid "可能是因为开启 Secure Boot 后 Bootloader 会变大，烧录固件时 Bin 文件产生了覆盖。 可以查询 Secure Boot 后 Bootloader 的大小，比如可以尝试把分区表的偏移量增大为 0xF000 。"
msgstr "This may be because the Bootloader becomes larger after Secure Boot is enabled, and the bin file overlaps when flashing the firmware. You can check the Bootloader size after Secure Boot is enabled. For example, try increasing the partition table offset to 0xF000."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:341 5e8f62eb5ab74cb1a0bc0bd853ab80e7
msgid "ESP8266 如何在设备软重启的情况下保留数据？"
msgstr "How can ESP8266 retain data when the device performs a soft reboot?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:343 225c9f8dff3e424cb86b9abdfff02a6a
msgid "如果写入或者修改的次数不频繁， 可以使用 Flash 来存储数据，该区域相对于内存较大，并且容易调整。"
msgstr "If writes or modifications are infrequent, Flash can be used to store data. This area is relatively larger than memory and is easy to adjust."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:344 fa075a0879c141db8f3c9875e687ff1b
msgid "若数据较小，可以使用 RTC Memory 内存来存储相关数据。示例： Rel 2.1 的分支中 esp_system.h 中的接口 （详细阅读使用说明）system_rtc_mem_read。"
msgstr "If the data is small, RTC Memory can be used to store related data. Example: the system_rtc_mem_read interface in esp_system.h in the Rel 2.1 branch (read the usage instructions carefully)."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:345 cf11078c620a42cfb7336247b5a9decb
msgid "如果以上两者都无法满足需求，也可以选择外挂的 RTC 内存，可以使用 I2C 与 SPI 进行交互。"
msgstr "If neither of the above meets the requirements, you can also choose external RTC memory, which can interact via I2C or SPI."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:346 96b511f7a0164751bcae56fcc29edaad
msgid "通常在写入频率不高的情况下建议写入 Flash ， 因为该方法在硬断电时数据仍然正常。"
msgstr "Generally, when the write frequency is low, it is recommended to write to Flash, because data remains valid even after a hard power-off."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:351 19e20e7339ad491b9c1d7a2e2a25d146
msgid "ESP8266 有哪些定时器可用？"
msgstr "What timers are available on ESP8266?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:353 a4209ebaed8d460b8499f282bed36d19
msgid "ESP8266 有一个硬件定时器，可以产生中断，在 NONOS SDK 与 RTOS SDK 调用 API 略有不同。"
msgstr "ESP8266 has one hardware timer that can generate interrupts. The APIs called in NONOS SDK and RTOS SDK are slightly different."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:354 d61517734eb84f8ca3742a3e822d3808
msgid "软件定时器： - NONOS 中 API os_timer 是 DSR 处理，不能产⽣中断，但是可以产⽣任务，任务会按照普通等级排队。 - RTOS 中可以使用 freertos 中的软件定时器，使用方式更加灵活。"
msgstr "Software timers: - In NONOS, the API os_timer is handled by DSR and cannot generate interrupts, but it can generate tasks, which are queued at normal priority. - In RTOS, FreeRTOS software timers can be used, providing more flexible usage."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:361 624d4c7cf2764fbba8a8ac217c6fd2fe
msgid "ESP8266 的看⻔狗是什么作⽤？"
msgstr "What is the watchdog on ESP8266 used for?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:363 72088a8ac15a43be91769e22376ee833
msgid "为了提供系统稳定性，以应对多冲突的操作环境，ESP8266 集成了 2 级看⻔狗机制，包括软件看⻔狗和硬件看⻔狗。"
msgstr "To provide system stability in operating environments with many conflicts, ESP8266 integrates a two-level watchdog mechanism, including a software watchdog and a hardware watchdog."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:364 714754dbbf9b4dd5b9cc67c30e0b8774
msgid "默认 2 个看⻔狗都是打开的，HW WDT 始终在运行，并且如果未重置 HW WDT 计时器，则会在大约 6 秒钟后重置 MCU。"
msgstr "Both watchdogs are enabled by default. HW WDT always runs, and if the HW WDT timer is not reset, it resets the MCU after about 6 seconds."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:365 d95012ec585446a2bfbfa39fc018ef19
msgid "SW WDT 大约在 1.5 秒左右将 MCU 复位。您可以启用/禁用 SW WDT，但不能启用/禁用 HW WDT。因为必须重置 SW WDT 后才能同时重置 HW WDT。"
msgstr "SW WDT resets the MCU after about 1.5 seconds. You can enable/disable SW WDT, but you cannot enable/disable HW WDT, because HW WDT can only be reset after SW WDT is reset."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:366 3eecc90e8b7a4955b2ea643a14229eaa
msgid "可通过修改 `make menuconfig` -> `Component config` -> `Common ESP-related` 里的 `Invoke panic handler on Task Watchdog timeout` 等来配置看门狗。"
msgstr "The watchdog can be configured by modifying items such as `Invoke panic handler on Task Watchdog timeout` under `make menuconfig` -> `Component config` -> `Common ESP-related`."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:371 974b3554fd7648b89638f84f2bc8ae50
msgid "ESP8266 user_init 内有那些注意事项？"
msgstr "What precautions are there in ESP8266 user_init?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:373 8ce9dd4c23dd4e3684c42930e22a8971
msgid "wifi_set_ip_info、wifi_set_macaddr 仅在 user_init 中调⽤⽣效，其他地⽅调⽤不⽣效。"
msgstr "wifi_set_ip_info and wifi_set_macaddr only take effect when called in user_init; calls elsewhere do not take effect."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:374 86d498c2777748219eb3f50fd03e4581
msgid "system_timer_reinit 建议在 user_init 中调⽤，否则调⽤后，需要重新 arm 所有 timer。"
msgstr "system_timer_reinit is recommended to be called in user_init; otherwise, after calling it, all timers need to be armed again."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:375 aba8e9166c2b4686953ea2f85fa42204
msgid "wifi_station_set_config 如果在 user_init 中调⽤，底层会⾃动连接对应路由，不需要再调⽤ wifi_station_connect 来进⾏连接。否则，需要调⽤ wifi_station_connect进⾏连接。"
msgstr "If wifi_station_set_config is called in user_init, the underlying layer will automatically connect to the corresponding router, and wifi_station_connect does not need to be called again. Otherwise, wifi_station_connect must be called to connect."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:376 6a64e5945294493fb0e68fc81c693c7b
msgid "wifi_station_set_auto_connect 设置上电启动时是否⾃动连接已记录的路由；例如，关闭⾃动连接功能，如果在 user_init 中调⽤，则当前这次上电就不会⾃动连接路由，如果在其他位置调⽤，则下次上电启动不会⾃动连接路由。"
msgstr "wifi_station_set_auto_connect sets whether to automatically connect to a recorded router after power-on startup. For example, if the automatic connection function is disabled and called in user_init, the device will not automatically connect to the router during the current power-on. If called elsewhere, it will not automatically connect to the router at the next power-on startup."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:381 488adba7d18848edb45f7bb60f5c68c8
msgid "ESP32 同时开启 \"Enable debug tracing of PM using GPIOs\" 和 \"Allow .bss segment placed in external memory\" 后为何会导致系统不停重启？"
msgstr "Why does ESP32 keep rebooting when both \"Enable debug tracing of PM using GPIOs\" and \"Allow .bss segment placed in external memory\" are enabled?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:383 d9f12fc42e6148c78d039753b536bc02
msgid "\"Enable debug tracing of PM using GPIOs\" 配置选项是在 GDB 调试时需要打开的，不可与 \"Allow .bss segment placed in external memory\" 配置选项同时使用。"
msgstr "The \"Enable debug tracing of PM using GPIOs\" configuration option is required during GDB debugging and cannot be used together with the \"Allow .bss segment placed in external memory\" configuration option."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:384 303936a60415455198a8caca98e0526b
msgid "因为 “Enable debug tracing of PM using GPIOs\" 默认使用的是 GPIO16 与 GPIO17 ，与 PSRAM 接口（默认也是 GPIO16 和 GPIO17） 冲突。"
msgstr "This is because “Enable debug tracing of PM using GPIOs\" uses GPIO16 and GPIO17 by default, which conflict with the PSRAM interface (also GPIO16 and GPIO17 by default)."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:388 ac14d5588dd54b549d32a694da913d56
msgid "ESP32 IDF v3.3 版本 bootloader 运行 v3.1 版本 APP bin , 程序为何会触发 RTCWDT_RTC_RESET ？"
msgstr "Why does an ESP32 IDF v3.3 bootloader running a v3.1 APP bin trigger RTCWDT_RTC_RESET?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:390 4b77d7389d574a9ba9932fe5f0671518
msgid "在 v3.3 的 bootloader 中会开启 WDT 看门狗，且在应用程序(app) 运行时关闭 WDT 看门狗。"
msgstr "In the v3.3 bootloader, the WDT watchdog is enabled, and the WDT watchdog is disabled when the application program (app) runs."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:391 e5ae63f87cec4c6ab0eec37ae504862f
msgid "但 v3.1 的 bootloader 没有开启 WDT 看门狗，所以应用程序(app) 没有 WDT 看门狗的机制，进而导致 v3.3 的 bootloader 引导 v3.1 的应用程序(app) 会触发 WDT 看门狗复位。"
msgstr "However, the v3.1 bootloader does not enable the WDT watchdog, so the application program (app) does not have a WDT watchdog mechanism. As a result, when the v3.3 bootloader boots the v3.1 application program (app), a WDT watchdog reset is triggered."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:392 e64600a648c949d78a9ba995bdb65924
msgid "可以通过在 menuconfig 中不使能 BOOTLOADER_WDT_ENABLE ，关闭 v3.3 版本 bootloader 中 WDT 看门狗开启。"
msgstr "You can disable BOOTLOADER_WDT_ENABLE in menuconfig to disable the WDT watchdog in the v3.3 bootloader."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:397 48b0c6997b6b4fd99e9d30cdd6a5bc93
msgid "ESP32 芯片出厂是否有唯一的 chip_id ？"
msgstr "Does the ESP32 chip have a unique chip_id when it leaves the factory?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:399 b913836ec27f4ac49487dcc1c5c17d8b
msgid "ESP32 芯片未未烧录唯一 chip_id，但设备默认烧录有全球唯一 MAC 地址，可以读取 MAC 地址替代 chip_id。"
msgstr "The ESP32 chip is not burned with a unique chip_id, but the device is burned with a globally unique MAC address by default. The MAC address can be read and used instead of chip_id."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:404 e7904d1881c64597a4b4eb31e8036adf
msgid "ESP8266 rst curse 如何查看？"
msgstr "How to check the ESP8266 reset cause?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:406 218433ed95cf45889a77debfcf126936
msgid "请参考 `ESP8266 异常重启原因 <https://www.espressif.com/sites/default/files/documentation/esp8266_reset_causes_and_common_fatal_exception_causes_cn.pdf/>`_。"
msgstr "Please refer to `ESP8266 Reset Causes and Common Fatal Exception Causes <https://www.espressif.com/sites/default/files/documentation/esp8266_reset_causes_and_common_fatal_exception_causes_cn.pdf/>`_."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:411 bcdbb0d7f365455c9f3e4cca76f24df7
msgid "ESP32 编译生成的 bin 文件大小如何优化？"
msgstr "How to optimize the size of bin files generated by ESP32 compilation?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:413 2bf13ac756ef46f2acdef40140052b1c
msgid "可配置 GCC 编译优化，操作步骤：idf.py menuconfig---->Compiler options---->Optimization level (Optimize for size(-Os))。"
msgstr "Configure GCC compilation optimization. Steps: idf.py menuconfig---->Compiler options---->Optimization level (Optimize for size(-Os))."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:414 39404d744ed44a62b606ff4eed08bba4
msgid "可对代码进行优化，提高代码复用率，调整 log 等级，减少不必要的 log 打印。"
msgstr "Optimize the code, improve code reuse, adjust the log level, and reduce unnecessary log printing."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:420 01b9c09166d241a58e8e062a90c7360d
msgid "ESP32 是否有系统重新启动的 API ？"
msgstr "Does ESP32 have an API for system restart?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:422 a9b465a0bb1f4e2b9ece0933ea4ead5a
msgid "系统重新启动的 API 可使用 esp_restart()，相关说明可 `参见 <https://docs.espressif.com/projects/esp-idf/zh_CN/latest/esp32/api-reference/system/ota.html?highlight=esp_restart#id5>`__ 。"
msgstr "The system restart API can use esp_restart(). Related instructions can be `referenced here <https://docs.espressif.com/projects/esp-idf/zh_CN/latest/esp32/api-reference/system/ota.html?highlight=esp_restart#id5>`__."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:427 41a9d7852a1142cb9c38b794aa2f8dc2
msgid "ESP32 异常 log `invalid header: 0xffffffff`"
msgstr "ESP32 abnormal log `invalid header: 0xffffffff`"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:429 26222e8745ae4ba5a77fe2ad0df0c630
msgid "ESP32 芯片打印该异常 log 通常有如下几种情况："
msgstr "ESP32 usually prints this abnormal log in the following cases:"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:430 8bd3b489c80143998eca83050d6580b0
msgid "芯片上下电时序不正确，芯片部分区域未完全复位。"
msgstr "The chip power-on/off sequence is incorrect, and some areas of the chip are not fully reset."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:431 dc779d61479b41379e89be6853cdb43c
msgid "Flash 中的固件出现异常，例如未烧录完整固件。"
msgstr "The firmware in Flash is abnormal, for example, the firmware was not completely flashed."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:432 4617bd1264c04c76b2a4223ff997b7bc
msgid "Flash 器件损坏，无法读取正确数据。"
msgstr "The Flash device is damaged and cannot read correct data."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:433 eda412345dc74fdeb5042defc81a5e3b
msgid "芯片自身 cache 被关闭或者损坏，无法读取固件数据。"
msgstr "The chip cache itself is disabled or damaged and cannot read firmware data."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:438 dc008899436743a1bfac73e418c2bd55
msgid "ESP8266 deep sleep 定时唤醒机制是什么？"
msgstr "What is the timed wake-up mechanism for ESP8266 deep sleep?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:440 f18f20efa52b4e7ab0bcbf0c2eaaf8d5
msgid "在 Deep-sleep 状态下，将 GPIO16 (XPD_DCDC) 连接至 EXT_RSTB ,计时到达睡眠时间后，GPIO16 输出低电平给 EXT_RSTB 管脚，芯片被复位唤醒。"
msgstr "In Deep-sleep mode, connect GPIO16 (XPD_DCDC) to EXT_RSTB. When the timer reaches the configured sleep duration, GPIO16 outputs a low level to the EXT_RSTB pin, and the chip is reset and woken up."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:443 7706fc84303843339e82694be64366f1
msgid "ESP32 使用 heap_caps_get_free_size 获取 RAM 约 300 KB，为何与手册 520K 存在差异？"
msgstr "Why does ESP32 report about 300 KB RAM using heap_caps_get_free_size, which differs from the 520 KB in the manual?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:445 adae917229364941897a9149cedbda22
msgid "是因为内存在系统启动时预分配给各个功能模块使用，系统启动后剩余内存约 300 KB。"
msgstr "This is because memory is pre-allocated to various functional modules during system startup. After the system starts, the remaining memory is about 300 KB."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:446 a29b0ea812424117a92308c781fd71fe
msgid "如果剩余内存不足，可以选用带 PSRAM 模组，将内存分配在 PSRAM 中。"
msgstr "If the remaining memory is insufficient, you can choose a module with PSRAM and allocate memory in PSRAM."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:451 19236942e02b41428bab5d9314a00640
msgid "ESP32 & ESP8266 如何通过局域网的 APP 进行 OTA 升级？"
msgstr "How can ESP32 & ESP8266 perform OTA upgrade through an APP on the LAN?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:453 a24fd51635b7442f84381e9afe61086a
msgid "局域网内 APP 设备可以配置开启 http 服务，将提供的固件下载链接通过其他方法（udp，coap，mqtt 等）发送至设备。"
msgstr "APP devices on the LAN can be configured to enable an HTTP service, and send the provided firmware download link to the device through other methods, such as UDP, CoAP, MQTT, etc."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:454 1ffd2a03cc17424f829cec34cff8c9c5
msgid "设备通过传统 URL OTA 方法即可完成 OTA 更新，示例已在 SDK 中提供。"
msgstr "The device can complete the OTA update through the traditional URL OTA method. Examples are already provided in the SDK."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:459 eed296255a004284a7cbde7528deed60
msgid "ESP32 如何修改 LOG 输出至串口 UART1 ?"
msgstr "How to change ESP32 LOG output to serial port UART1?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:461 2ae00f2fd2854ad8b809f045d6ad8ff4
msgid "更换 LOG 输出串口为 UART1 可通过配置 menuconfig -> Component Config ->Common ESP-related -> Channel for console output -> Custom UART -> UART peripheral to use for console output(0-1) -> UART1"
msgstr "To change the LOG output serial port to UART1, configure: menuconfig -> Component Config -> Common ESP-related -> Channel for console output -> Custom UART -> UART peripheral to use for console output(0-1) -> UART1"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:466 0852fd6ffbd44c1297073a99558e976b
msgid "ESP8266 使用 MQTT ssl_mutual_auth 通讯，在 OTA 时出现如下报错："
msgstr "ESP8266 uses MQTT ssl_mutual_auth communication, and the following error occurs during OTA:"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:477 33056cdb98424598b5e5c276c6dd4bb0
msgid "0x7f00 此报错是由于 内存不足 导致，建议使用 http 方式 OTA 。"
msgstr "The 0x7f00 error is caused by insufficient memory. It is recommended to use HTTP for OTA."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:482 6868be8d35804a18b5986bd6de8cd5f0
msgid "ESP32 配置 menuconfig --> Component config 中有 NVS 选项，为何配置项目为空？"
msgstr "ESP32 has an NVS option under menuconfig --> Component config. Why is the configuration item empty?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:484 93e7eb7dae9a49149499797715bc10db
msgid "menuconfig --> Component config 中的 NVS 选项是配置 NVS 加密功能的，该功能的前提是开启 Flash 加密。"
msgstr "The NVS option under menuconfig --> Component config is used to configure the NVS encryption function. This function requires Flash encryption to be enabled first."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:485 2bf1232a64e5420f8d2cb52dcc7e44ca
msgid "menuconfig --> security feaures --> enable flash encryption on boot 配置选项后，便可以看到 NVS 的配置选项。"
msgstr "After configuring menuconfig --> security feaures --> enable flash encryption on boot, the NVS configuration options will be visible."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:490 eb7f72094c3441a1bc2eae2f48042777
msgid "ESP32 上电或 Deep-sleep 醒来后，会随机发⽣⼀次看⻔狗复位?"
msgstr "Will ESP32 randomly experience a watchdog reset once after power-on or waking up from Deep-sleep?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:492 b1938fd1dee14263a7860ee4382e5c5a
msgid "芯⽚上电的看⻔狗复位⽆法使⽤软件绕过，但复位后 ESP32 正常启动。"
msgstr "The watchdog reset on chip power-on cannot be bypassed by software, but ESP32 starts normally after the reset."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:493 d2a8e6397cba48c49deab0b9727c0ae7
msgid "Deep-sleep 醒来后的看⻔狗复位在 ESP-IDF V1.0 及更⾼版本中⾃动绕过。"
msgstr "The watchdog reset after waking up from Deep-sleep is automatically bypassed in ESP-IDF V1.0 and later versions."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:494 ff9761d3276a4061a48f1f3c1693c40a
msgid "Deep-sleep 醒来后，CPU 可以⽴即执⾏ RTC fast memory 中的⼀段程序。RTC fast memory 中的这段程序通过清除 cache MMU 的⾮法访问标志从⽽绕过 Deep-sleep 醒来后的看⻔狗复位，具体为："
msgstr "After waking up from Deep-sleep, the CPU can immediately execute a piece of program in RTC fast memory. This program in RTC fast memory bypasses the watchdog reset after Deep-sleep wake-up by clearing the illegal access flag of the cache MMU, specifically by:"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:496 4a4cac90a3d047a484ebe4dd0f76544c
msgid "将 DPORT_PRO_CACHE_CTRL1_REG 寄存器的 PRO_CACHE_MMU_IA_CLR ⽐特置 1。"
msgstr "Setting the PRO_CACHE_MMU_IA_CLR bit of the DPORT_PRO_CACHE_CTRL1_REG register to 1."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:497 84ba2ff52f7f4b3fbabdba3a29c17fa3
msgid "将该⽐特清零。"
msgstr "Clearing this bit to 0."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:502 d096ea95addf4585b836f14710990922
msgid "ESP32 CPU 使⽤ cache 访问外部 SRAM 时，如果这些操作需要 CPU 同时处理，可能会发⽣读写错误?"
msgstr "When ESP32 CPU accesses external SRAM through cache, read/write errors may occur if these operations need to be processed by the CPU at the same time?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:504 d2bf914c00ad4ecdad65fc6c031291ea
msgid "这个问题⽆法使⽤软件⾃动绕过。"
msgstr "This issue cannot be automatically bypassed by software."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:505 1d35b1aa160143fba42a64d850b849dc
msgid "对于版本 0 ESP32，CPU 使⽤ cache 访问外部 SRAM 时，只能够进⾏单向操作，即只能够单纯的进⾏写 SRAM 操作，或者单纯的进⾏读 SRAM 操作，不能交替操作。"
msgstr "For version 0 ESP32, when the CPU accesses external SRAM through cache, only one-way operations can be performed. That is, it can only perform pure SRAM write operations or pure SRAM read operations, but cannot alternate between them."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:506 3aaed73029ed4bcca4acd526737fc655
msgid "使⽤ MEMW 指令：在读操作之后，加上 ``__asm__(\"MEMW\")`` 指令，然后在 CPU 流⽔线被清空前再发起写操作。"
msgstr "Use the MEMW instruction: after a read operation, add the ``__asm__(\"MEMW\")`` instruction, and then initiate a write operation before the CPU pipeline is flushed."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:511 2137cc7910d54d769458fddc42de4867
msgid "ESP32 CPU 访问外设时，如果连续不间断地通过 DPORT 写同⼀个地址，为何会出现数据丢失的现象？"
msgstr "Why does data loss occur when ESP32 CPU accesses peripherals and continuously writes the same address through DPORT without interruption?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:513 63f95f91fbd9484abc1fe82b34588d4a
msgid "此问题在 ESP-IDF V1.0 及更⾼版本中⾃动绕过。"
msgstr "This issue is automatically bypassed in ESP-IDF V1.0 and later versions."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:514 c94f0a4ce59b4be5bb98bcfd3af69801
msgid "当连续写同⼀个地址（即类似 FIFO 的地址）时，使⽤ AHB 地址⽽不是 DPORT 地址。（对于其他类型的寄存器写⼊，使⽤ DPORT 地址可能写性能更好。）"
msgstr "When continuously writing to the same address, such as a FIFO-like address, use the AHB address instead of the DPORT address. For other types of register writes, using the DPORT address may provide better write performance."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:517 18272cfc020a459caa684a11bf0071f9
msgid "寄存器名称"
msgstr "Register Name"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:517 36d2de127f514d77813b4e9646bf3fc7
msgid "DPORT 地址"
msgstr "DPORT Address"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:517 4b98002d5d9b4ab490a34b1a7b18b71d
msgid "AHB（安全）地址"
msgstr "AHB (Secure) Address"

