#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:553 67eba18e65e242789080c955a73046be
msgid "ESP32 CPU 频率从 240 MHz 直接切换到 80/160 MHz 会卡死，如何解决？"
msgstr "How to solve the issue that the ESP32 CPU freezes when switching directly from 240 MHz to 80/160 MHz?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:555 2b5a00e7d39c49bba4d3be525dc383ae
msgid "建议使⽤以下两种模式："
msgstr "It is recommended to use one of the following two switching modes:"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:557 6615d32602b14482bb73dbaec5e31148
msgid "2 MHz <-> 40 MHz <-> 80 MHz <-> 160 MHz"
msgstr "2 MHz <-> 40 MHz <-> 80 MHz <-> 160 MHz"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:558 b804ef1b30e04933a43e8942621ed1c2
msgid "2 MHz <->40 MHz <->240 MHz"
msgstr "2 MHz <-> 40 MHz <-> 240 MHz"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:559 ec597e0cdd65411882703da8cb842816
msgid "此问题已在芯⽚版本 1 中修复。"
msgstr "This issue has been fixed in chip revision 1."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:564 7991785d846e468898ba8751e061acba
msgid "ESP32 同时有 GPIO 和 RTC_GPIO 功能的 pad 的上拉下拉电阻只能由 RTC_GPIO 的上拉下拉寄存器控制，如何解决？"
msgstr "For ESP32 pads that have both GPIO and RTC_GPIO functions, the pull-up and pull-down resistors can only be controlled by RTC_GPIO pull-up/pull-down registers. How to solve this?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:566 23dbc6f568c945b6b1a92c714ac4641f
msgid "ESP-IDF V2.1 及更⾼版本的 GPIO 驱动⾃动绕过此问题。"
msgstr "The GPIO driver in ESP-IDF V2.1 and later automatically works around this issue."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:567 9dd684e5a38e41f6a7427b8755c599e6
msgid "GPIO 和 RTC_GPIO 都使⽤ RTC_GPIO 寄存器。"
msgstr "Both GPIO and RTC_GPIO use RTC_GPIO registers."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:572 18eb0b2881cd4559847d5fd7fa31489a
msgid "ESP32 由于 flash 启动的速度慢于芯⽚读取 flash 的速度，芯⽚上电或 Deep-sleep 醒来后，会随机发⽣⼀次看⻔狗复位，如何解决？"
msgstr "Because the flash startup speed is slower than the chip's flash read speed, the ESP32 may randomly trigger a watchdog reset once after power-on or waking up from Deep-sleep. How to solve this?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:574 fb509e0b28554086866d87e575bb95b2
msgid "更换更快的 flash，要求 flash 上电到可读的时间⼩于 800 μs。这种⽅法可以绕过芯⽚上电和 Deep-sleep 醒来时的看⻔狗复位。"
msgstr "Replace the flash with a faster one. The flash must be readable within 800 μs after power-on. This method can work around the watchdog reset during chip power-on and wake-up from Deep-sleep."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:575 4eb000a46431419fa36988b177d758c4
msgid "Deep-sleep 醒来后的看⻔狗复位问题在 ESP-IDF V2.0 及更⾼版本中⾃动绕过（延迟时间可以根据需要配置）。具体⽅式是从 Deep-sleep 醒来后⾸先读取 RTC fast memory 中的指令，等待⼀段时间，然后再读取 flash。"
msgstr "The watchdog reset issue after waking up from Deep-sleep is automatically worked around in ESP-IDF V2.0 and later. The delay time can be configured as needed. Specifically, after waking up from Deep-sleep, instructions are first read from RTC fast memory, then the system waits for a period of time before reading from flash."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:580 f0806dbe746a4bfa85df4d3e6b1d5155
msgid "ESP32 CPU 在访问外部 SRAM 时会⼩概率发⽣读写错误, 如何解决？"
msgstr "The ESP32 CPU may occasionally encounter read/write errors when accessing external SRAM. How to solve this?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:588 9972fea8f8434de5894050f0bbb35429
msgid "x>=y 时，在 store.x 和 load.y 之间插⼊ 4 个 nop 指令。"
msgstr "When x >= y, insert 4 nop instructions between store.x and load.y."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:589 da309fdba6574bacbfc0c5f064b3e1fe
msgid "x<y 时，在 store.x 和 load.y 之间插⼊ memw 指令。"
msgstr "When x < y, insert a memw instruction between store.x and load.y."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:594 84b0dc8ade0448f5ba94d4397b723878
msgid "ESP32 双核情况下，⼀个 CPU 的总线在读 A 地址空间，⽽另⼀个 CPU 的总线在读 B 地址空间，读 B 地址空间的 CPU可能会发⽣错误如何解决？"
msgstr "In ESP32 dual-core mode, when one CPU bus is reading address space A while another CPU bus is reading address space B, the CPU reading address space B may encounter an error. How to solve this?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:596 2d1754941afa43ffbf1a3bbc43c7969b
msgid "⼀个 CPU 在读 A 地址空间时，通过加锁和中断的⽅式来避免另⼀个 CPU 发起对 B 地址空间的读操作。"
msgstr "When one CPU is reading address space A, prevent the other CPU from initiating a read operation to address space B by using locks and interrupts."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:597 1e9ca31cacbe440aa48cacb010af0805
msgid "⼀个 CPU 在读 A 地址空间之前，加⼀个此 CPU 读 B 地址空间（⾮ FIFO 地址空间，如 0x3FF40078）操作，并且要保证读 B 地址空间操作和读 A 地址空间操作是原⼦的。"
msgstr "Before one CPU reads address space A, add an operation where this CPU reads address space B first, using a non-FIFO address space such as 0x3FF40078. Ensure that the read operation to address space B and the read operation to address space A are atomic."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:602 e706e6cfd8b24cf790a7d459cc50ba10
msgid "ESP32 CPU 通过读取 INTERRUPT_REG 寄存器来复位 CAN 控制器的中断信号。如果在同⼀个 APB 时钟周期内 CAN 控制器刚好产⽣发送中断信号，则发送中断信号丢失，如何解决？"
msgstr "The ESP32 CPU resets the interrupt signal of the CAN controller by reading the INTERRUPT_REG register. If the CAN controller happens to generate a transmit interrupt signal in the same APB clock cycle, the transmit interrupt signal will be lost. How to solve this?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:604 05241216a8cb46269536794cfa5cfac4
msgid "数据等待发送完成期间（即发送请求已发起），每⼀次读取 INTERRUPT_REG 后，⽤户都应检查 ``STATUS_TRANSMIT_BUFFER`` 位。如果 ``STATUS_TRANSMIT_BUFFER`` 置位⽽ ``CAN_TRANSMIT_INT_ST`` 没有置位，则说明发送中断信号丢失。"
msgstr "During the period when data is waiting to be sent, that is, after a transmit request has been initiated, the user should check the ``STATUS_TRANSMIT_BUFFER`` bit after every read of INTERRUPT_REG. If ``STATUS_TRANSMIT_BUFFER`` is set while ``CAN_TRANSMIT_INT_ST`` is not set, it indicates that the transmit interrupt signal has been lost."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:610 9ac8ca6edb0c4b48983d646a054a8230
msgid "ESP32 ECO V3 芯⽚，当程序同时满⾜下列条件时，会出现 live lock（活锁）现象，导致 CPU ⼀直处于访存状态，不能继续执⾏指令，请问如何解决？"
msgstr "For the ESP32 ECO V3 chip, when the program meets the following conditions simultaneously, a live lock may occur, causing the CPU to remain in memory access state and unable to continue executing instructions. How to solve this?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:618 91b55872ba494cdabd3def9dc6e560c4
msgid "发⽣ live lock 时，软件主动或被动识别并解锁 cache line 竞争，之后两个核按队列节拍分时完成各⾃的 cache 操作，解锁 live lock。详细过程如下："
msgstr "When live lock occurs, software actively or passively identifies and releases cache line contention. Then the two cores complete their respective cache operations in time slices according to queue timing, thereby unlocking the live lock. The detailed process is as follows:"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:620 f7ab0c6ed5524058990df7bcec499a94
msgid "当两个核执⾏的指令均不在代码临界区中时出现 live lock，系统各类型中断会主动解除 cache line 竞争，解锁 live lock；"
msgstr "If live lock occurs when the instructions executed by both cores are not in the code critical section, system interrupts of various types will actively release cache line contention and unlock the live lock;"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:621 ccfc43014866416396ce2f2371568dcf
msgid "当两个核执⾏的指令位于代码临界区中时出现 live lock，在临界区中，系统会屏蔽 3 级及以下中断。因此软件预先为两个核各设置⼀个⾼优先级（4 级或 5 级）中断，将它们绑定到同⼀个定时器，并选择合适的定时器超时⻔限。由于 live lock 产⽣的定时器超时中断会迫使两个核均进⼊⾼优先级中断处理程序，从⽽释放两个核的 IBUS 以达到解锁 live lock ⽬的。解锁过程通过 3 个阶段完成："
msgstr "If live lock occurs when the instructions executed by both cores are in the code critical section, level 3 and lower interrupts are masked in the critical section. Therefore, software pre-configures a high-priority interrupt, level 4 or level 5, for each core, binds both interrupts to the same timer, and selects an appropriate timer timeout threshold. The timer timeout interrupt caused by live lock forces both cores to enter the high-priority interrupt handler, thereby releasing the IBUS of both cores to unlock the live lock. The unlocking process is completed in three stages:"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:623 57c2b1486fe64b7ab9d4415040ddaec2
msgid "第 1 阶段两个核均进⾏等待以清空 CPU write buffer；"
msgstr "In stage 1, both cores wait to clear the CPU write buffer;"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:624 8248d568e447456b8f28266506d266ae
msgid "第 2 阶段⼀个核 (Core 0) 等待，另⼀个核 (Core 1) 执⾏；"
msgstr "In stage 2, one core (Core 0) waits while the other core (Core 1) executes;"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:625 151d391f201b4c94a50ddf00c7610a49
msgid "第 3 阶段 Core 1 等待，Core 0 执⾏。"
msgstr "In stage 3, Core 1 waits while Core 0 executes."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:630 59dac07826b84ab9800b2076591ec08c
msgid "ESP32 CPU 访问 ``0x3FF0_0000 ~ 0x3FF1_EFFF`` 与 ``0x3FF4_0000 ~ 0x3FF7_FFFF`` 两段地址空间存在限制，如何解决？"
msgstr "The ESP32 CPU has access restrictions for the address ranges ``0x3FF0_0000 ~ 0x3FF1_EFFF`` and ``0x3FF4_0000 ~ 0x3FF7_FFFF``. How to solve this?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:632 3459b314b5154f3fac42264182b8b705
msgid "落在这两段地址空间的 CPU 访问均需要在对应的操作前加⼊ “MEMW” 指令。即在 C/C++ 中，软件访问这两段地址内的寄存器时需要加上 “volatile” 属性。"
msgstr "CPU accesses that fall within these two address ranges require a “MEMW” instruction before the corresponding operation. That is, in C/C++, when software accesses registers within these two address ranges, the “volatile” attribute must be added."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:637 69a48bbd7cd34838820611b1e29dcd3a
msgid "ESP32 如何关闭程序 LOG 输出？"
msgstr "How to disable program LOG output on ESP32?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:639 2d29e4f8b1c540098e7b126240c93734
msgid "关闭 bootloader 日志：menuconfig -> bootloader config --> bootloader log verbosity 选定为 No output 。"
msgstr "Disable bootloader logs: menuconfig -> bootloader config --> bootloader log verbosity, select No output."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:640 e5b92eb1ce9b447990dd8f7c80532297
msgid "关闭程序日志：menuconfig -> Component config --> log output --> Default log verbosity 选定为 No output 。"
msgstr "Disable application logs: menuconfig -> Component config --> log output --> Default log verbosity, select No output."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:641 27e27162522248c486d7b13b908d7057
msgid "关闭 UART0 输出日志：menuconfig -> Component Config ->Common ESP-related -> Channel for console output -> None 。"
msgstr "Disable UART0 log output: menuconfig -> Component Config -> Common ESP-related -> Channel for console output -> None."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:645 f1993d5ab5164e45833190313ddbde19
msgid "ESP-15F模组支持microbit之类的单片机编程吗"
msgstr "Does the ESP-15F module support programming with microcontroller boards such as micro:bit?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:646 76096850423441f7b02c04ce70778ef3
msgid "支持"
msgstr "Supported."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:649 207eb3b0236f46248ffe737305b1ad22
msgid "ESP-12F模组能装操作系统吗"
msgstr "Can the ESP-12F module run an operating system?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:650 83b13946138e4b97b4daa15983246a6e
msgid "可以装FreeRTOS实时操作系统"
msgstr "It can run the FreeRTOS real-time operating system."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:653 73fb2fe159d94b8191ca1a8583923646
msgid "请问ESP-12F模组如何搭建开发环境呢？"
msgstr "How to set up the development environment for the ESP-12F module?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/system.rst:654 7093ae70b9bb450193112193e9f41de9
msgid "`参考链接 <https://docs.espressif.com/projects/esp8266-rtos-sdk/en/latest/get-started/index.html#setup-toolchain>`__（该说明文档没有中文版的）"
